## Algorithm Analysis

### Time Complexity
- **Best Case:** O(n) - when array is already sorted
- **Average Case:** O(nÂ²) 
- **Worst Case:** O(nÂ²) - when array is reverse sorted

### Space Complexity
- **O(1)** - only uses a constant amount of extra space

